This is a list of bugs in the Everything2.com xml output:

xmltrue displaytype for user nodetype:
	The number of C!s used is reported incorrectly.
	Bookmark titles are not escaped.

bestusers XML ticker:
	ebu_noadmins parameter is ignored in favor of whatever the user last
	set the "don't show monkeys" checkbox to in "Everything's Best Users"

coolnodes XML ticker:
	Username should be escaped (try loading the ticker with 
	cooledby=halcyon%26on).
	Node title should be escaped (try loading the ticker with
	cooledby=).stupidfawn.( -- this chokes on &hearts;).

